  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.8.2">
<l>vāta māmakaṉ markkaṭam vilaṅku maṟṟōr cātiyeṉ ṟoḻintilai yukantu</l>
<l>kāta lātaraṅ kaṭaliṉum perukac ceyta kaviṉuk killaikai<supplied>m</supplied>mā  ṟeṉṟu</l>
<l>kōtil vāymaiyi ṉāyoṭu muṭaṉē yuṇpaṉ nāṉeṉṟa vōṇporu ḷeṉakkum</l>
<l>ātal vēṇṭumeṉ ṟaṭiyiṇai yaṭaintē ṉaṇipo ḻiltiru varaṅkattam māṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having [first] said, “The great son of the wind is a monkey;</l>
<l rend="indent">animals are another race,” rejoicing, you who did not forsake [him],</l>
<l>As love and longing swelled [like] the sea, [you] said,</l>
<l rend="indent">“There is no recompense for the value of [your] actions!”</l>
<l>Thinking I, too, need a splendorous event for me,</l>
<l rend="indent">that I enjoy [being] with you of blemishless speech,</l>
<l>I took refuge at your two feet, lord of sacred Araṅkam with lovely groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
